  "summary": "Malicious code in zyncmap (npm)",
  "details": "Zyncmap@0.0.0 is a trojanized SVG sanitizer package. The package presents a legitimate-looking SVG processing API (sanitize, minify, save, convert to PNG) but also exports a getPlugin() function that fetches a JSON payload from hxxps://www[.]jsonkeeper[.]com/b/3P9BF (with a custom HTTP header bearrtoken:logo) and evaluates the value of the 'model' field via eval(), enabling arbitrary remote code execution. The remote host is a third-party file-hosting service, not a legitimate installer destination.",
